title: Week 7 Studs & Duds +  Arthur the Goldfish, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/24
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason react to the biggest studs and duds of Week 7! Which surprising studs or duds can be trusted in fantasy football lineups going forward? Plus, big-time injury news, and the Week 7 edition of Monday Punday. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 24th, 2022.
